-- Saras Will Sell 250 Million Euros of Bonds To Refinance, Lengthen Debt
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-16T15:50:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/saras-will-sell-250-million-euros-of-bonds-to-refinance-lengthen-debt.html

          
          
             Saras Spa announced it will sell 250
million euros of bonds to refinance and extend debt maturity.  
 Saras will sell 5-year bonds with a 5.583 percent coupon.
Banca Imi, Unicredit and Banca Akros will manage the sale.  
          
          


  


        